{"tid":21241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[青春] 一人N樣中學痴線事","createTime":"2016-12-03T17:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T20:51:27.000Z","uid":33957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48d907d9fa66a8aebc0f2490aab3c1c673e8524b","tid":21241,"uid":33957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"我間中學真係癲佬既培養皿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係其中之一</span></span><br />\n食完lunch有break 之後要上堂<br />\n成班人可以一齊玩水玩撚到拉哂水喉<br />\n最後成層濕撚哂(得一個班房同校務處) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後拖乾用吹地機吹乾小小扮無野上堂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個個套校務都濕撚到透哂<br />\n老師問 我地話遇到水鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但grad左要約出黎真係難到仆街 約到口臭都無人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又好撚想同你班癲佬食飯吹水<br />\n<br />\np.s 勿相認"},{"pid":"d2ee290c9ef206e8ae11735bc880c20365762ea5","tid":21241,"uid":33957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間中學真係癲佬既培養皿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係其中之一</span></span><br />\n食完lunch有break 之後要上堂<br />\n成班人可以一齊玩水玩撚到拉哂水喉<br />\n最後成層濕撚哂(得一個班房同校務處) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後拖乾用吹地機吹乾小小扮無野上堂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個個套校<span style=\"